  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个目标管理的工作流，从定义目标开始，经过策略规划，最后验证是否达成。整体是一个循环迭代的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoalDefine",
        "StrategyPlan",
        "GoalValidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这是一个PDCA风格的循环。我理解为：先定义目标，然后规划策略，执行功能，最后验证。验证不通过的话要回到策略规划重新调整对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoalDefine",
        "StrategyPlan",
        "GoalValidate",
        "StrategyPlan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，关键是GoalValidate这里要有分支判断。如果验证失败，返回StrategyPlan重新规划；如果验证通过，就进入done状态结束流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoalValidate",
        "StrategyPlan",
        "done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主线：从GoalDefine到StrategyPlan，然后需要细化执行层。策略规划之后是不是直接执行功能？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GoalDefine",
        "StrategyPlan",
        "FunctionExecute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "策略规划之后有两个可能：直接执行功能，或者如果策略本身有问题，也可以直接结束。我需要一个FunctionExecute节点，以及FunctionValidate来验证执行结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StrategyPlan",
        "FunctionExecute",
        "FunctionValidate",
        "done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加FunctionExecute和FunctionValidate。现在FunctionValidate验证通过后应该到哪里？是直接进入GoalValidate吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FunctionExecute",
        "FunctionValidate",
        "GoalValidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不是直接到GoalValidate，中间还有一个StrategyValidate。功能验证通过后要先验证策略是否有效，策略验证通过后再验证目标是否达成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FunctionValidate",
        "StrategyValidate",
        "GoalValidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以链条是FunctionValidate → StrategyValidate → GoalValidate。那StrategyValidate如果失败呢？有哪些出口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FunctionValidate",
        "StrategyValidate",
        "GoalValidate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "StrategyValidate比较关键，它有三个出口：一是回到FunctionExecute重新执行，二是继续到GoalValidate，三是发现策略有问题时回到StrategyPlan重新规划。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StrategyValidate",
        "FunctionExecute",
        "GoalValidate",
        "StrategyPlan"
